      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "The COLOR command jumps SPF/PC to the 0.4 color selection panel"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "from anywhere.  Once a color is selected and the selections"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "panel is terminated, control is returned to the panel from where"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "COLOR was executed."
